name: faq-rent-I've found a place I want to rent. Now what?

messages.title: Is there anything I can help you with?

messages.speech: If you haven’t already, make sure you go and view the property. If it’s a house-share, meet all the people you’ll be moving in with. The letting agent will ask you to sign a Tenancy Fee Declaration form which lists the services they will provide and the fees expected from you. The agent will then begin the referencing process to ensure you’re in a position to rent the property
